Legacy and modern screenshot templates used multiple individual SCPI steps (9-13 steps each) that the Steps UI generator couldn't properly sequence. Missing timeout handling, missing error handling for directory creation.
Templates broke screenshot capture into individual save_waveform/scpi_write steps. The Steps UI doesn't handle complex multi-step sequences with timeout changes and error handling well. Using save_waveform type for FILESYSTEM:READFILE was a workaround that caused issues.
