The blockToStep converter did not properly translate Blockly connect_scope blocks into Steps UI connect steps with full device configuration (backend, IP, timeout, connectionType, deviceType).
Enhanced convertStepToBlock() in stepToBlock.ts to look up devices in the devices array by name, extract all configuration (backend, host, connectionType, deviceType, timeout), and populate connect steps with full device config.
